  "texts": [
    "Sequencing within the chat can also make a difference.",
    "Responses to prompts build off of the previous prompts within a chat to constantly optimize answers.",
    "For this reason, there is no 'undo' feature.",
    "Thus, one must be careful with when and how the prompting process develops in the research pipeline.",
    "To test the stability of the prompt when 'starting from scratch', it is best to enter the prompt in a new chat to examine the robustness of the prompt and qualitatively assess the discrepancy in the model's response."
